title: SpaceX streams video of Tesla Roadster floating through space
text:
SpaceX streams video of Tesla Roadster floating through space   00:31 
Elon Musk's cherry red Tesla Roadster automobile floats through space after it was carried there by SpaceX's Falcon Heavy, the rocket company said. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
